Package com.petpet.c3po.adaptor.rules

This package contains pre and post processing rules.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AssignCollectionToElementRule This PostProcessingRule applies the given collection to every Element that is processed.
CreateElementIdentifierRule A PostProcessingRule that creates an element uid if it was not created by adaptor for some reason.
EmptyValueProcessingRule A PreProcessingRule that skips the meta data records if their value is null or an empty string.
FormatVersionResolutionRule A post processing rule to correct a FITS reported conflict in the format version that was marked as ok.
HtmlInfoProcessingRule A PreProcessingRule that cleans up values provided by a special tool bundled in FITS by TU Wien.
InferDateFromFileNameRule A post processing rule that tries to infer the creation date of an object out of its name.
 

Package com.petpet.c3po.adaptor.rules Description
